raw_data.title: Principal Subject Matter Expert
raw_data.description: The Subject Matter Expert is called upon to examine highly complex technical issues and propose solutions to resolve those problems.  Expert advise may be applied to analyzing one or more areas in the design, development and implementation of products and systems.  A Subject Matter Expert has widespread engineering knowledge and is regarded as an expert in the field of one or more engineering specialties. Recommends modifications to development and design to enhance product quality or process flow. Typically reports to a manager or executive.  A Subject Matter Expert works on advanced, complex technical projects or business issues requiring state of the art technical or industry knowledge. Works autonomously. Goals are generally communicated in solution or project goal terms. May provide a leadership role for the work group through knowledge in the area of specialization.
